    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Meu primeiro bootstrap</h1>
   
<div class="container">
    <h2>Tabela Básica</h2>
    <p>A classe <code>table</code> adiciona um estilo básico (leve espaçamento e apenas divisores horizontais) a uma tabela:</p>
    <table class="table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome</th>
                <th>Sobrenome</th>
                <th>Email</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>João</td>
                <td>Silva</td>
                <td>joao@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Maria</td>
                <td>Santos</td>
                <td>maria@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Juliana</td>
                <td>Oliveira</td>
                <td>juliana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Tabela Listrada</h2>
    <p>Adicione <code>.table-striped</code> para criar uma tabela listrada:</p>
    <table class="table table-striped">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome</th>
                <th>Sobrenome</th>
                <th>Email</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>João</td>
                <td>Silva</td>
                <td>joao@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Maria</td>
                <td>Santos</td>
                <td>maria@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Juliana</td>
                <td>Oliveira</td>
                <td>juliana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Tabela com Bordas</h2>
    <p>Adicione <code>.table-bordered</code> para criar uma tabela com bordas:</p>
    <table class="table table-bordered">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome</th>
                <th>Sobrenome</th>
                <th>Email</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>João</td>
                <td>Silva</td>
                <td>joao@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Maria</td>
                <td>Santos</td>
                <td>maria@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Juliana</td>
                <td>Oliveira</td>
                <td>juliana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Tabela com Hover</h2>
    <p>Adicione <code>.table-hover</code> para habilitar o efeito de hover nas linhas da tabela:</p>
    <table class="table table-hover">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome</th>
                <th>Sobrenome</th>
                <th>Email</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>João</td>
                <td>Silva</td>
                <td>joao@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Maria</td>
                <td>Santos</td>
                <td>maria@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Juliana</td>
                <td>Oliveira</td>
                <td>juliana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Tabela com Classes Contextuais</h2>
    <p>Use classes contextuais para colorir linhas ou células da tabela:</p>
    <table class="table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome</th>
                <th>Sobrenome</th>
                <th>Email</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr class="table-primary">
                <td>João</td>
                <td>Silva</td>
                <td>joao@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="table-success">
                <td>Maria</td>
                <td>Santos</td>
                <td>maria@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="table-danger">
                <td>Juliana</td>
                <td>Oliveira</td>
                <td>juliana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="table-warning">
                <td>Ana</td>
                <td>Souza</td>
                <td>ana@example.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="table-info">
                <td>Pedro</td>
                <td>Almeida</td>
                <td>pedro@example.com</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
   
